{
  "stem": "3658.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there-- from there, they send us to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to-- to Camp Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was where the transport went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Mauthausen, when we arrived-- I don't remember how-- how long it took us to get there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We arrived to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was in Austria.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you imagine, Auschwitz was in-- in Poland, and Mauthausen was in Austria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You went by train?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was a terrible camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh my god, that was-- there was another [GERMAN], which was also crematoriums and gas chambers and so.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there, we stayed-- when I say 'we,' the-- it depends on what barrack you are in-- for a couple of weeks or three weeks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was a horrible camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember it very clearly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People were carrying stones, and then, they used to just put you-- shove you into the-- to a ravine, and then you die.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I didn't stay there long, two or three weeks maximum.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- then, we were marched to Gusen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked from there, which is not-- obviously wasn't that far.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Gusen I, it was called.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, each camp, as I went along, was worse than the one before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was a-- another terrible, terrible camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we stayed there for a few weeks, or it could be two or three months.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, the next camp was Gusen II.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We helped-- actually, they-- they build Gusen II to-- because they couldn't-- they couldn't get rid of the people fast enough by-- by gassing and killing them, so-- and all the time, the transports were coming, you know, from everywhere.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from there, we were taken to Gusen II.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to-- from Gusen I to Gusen II.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
